dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Clark_Hydro_2014.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Clark_HydroLine_2014' and 'Clark_HydroPoly_2014'. [Hydrography Spatial Database of Clark County Depicting Rivers and Lakes. Derived from 1997 ortho photos.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
